cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.DM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the problem of learning from imbalanced data set using an ensemble of classification tree and artificial neural network models. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed methodology involves sampling techniques and feature selection, which are also relevant to computational engineering (cs.CE) and data mining (cs.DM). Additionally, the use of artificial neural networks suggests a connection to neural networks (cs.NE) as well.
